    "title": "Porter is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "Porter invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of E-commerce Executive at our Patna location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Porter:\nPorter is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Porter!",
